, symmetry-broken states proposed for\nbilayers. This generalization also explains the systematic even-odd effect of\ninteractions in Bernal-stacked layers of different thickness that is emerging\nfrom experiments, and has implications for the multilayer-to-graphite\ncrossover.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Jan 2015 13:47:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-04"}
